    "description": "<i>你爬过一具又一具溺死的尸体，终于上了嶙峋险峻的海岸，身后的潮水乌黑如墨，头顶的海鸥惨声阵阵，鼻息之间尽是海草的腥气。若不是发生了奇迹，你断然无法踏上伊德拉的土地。此时此地，活命已然不易，揭破黑教的诡秘更需要你用尽浑身解数。 </i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069160/extras/7f0a52e296351293dbefa101ba7635e7.avif?t=1766090307\" width=620 height=230 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069160/extras/c544b4a1c20028bba8a7c1243c83eab2.avif?t=1766090307\" width=800 height=416 /></span><br><br>《SKALD：攻打黑修院》从老派角色扮演游戏中汲取灵感，具备现代的设计理念和引人入胜的叙事，同时融合了地道的 8-bit 游戏美术风格与风采。<br><br>深入黑暗的奇幻世界，应对夺人性命的危险生物，邂逅形形色色的悲情英雄，直面洛夫克拉夫特式的恐怖。踏上宏大的复古风格冒险之旅，尽情探索，在回合制战术对战中大展身手。<br><br>你是否有能力带着一众落魄的英雄，走出伊德拉污秽不堪的海岸，打进黑教的修院，探索当中的奥秘？ <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069160/extras/50683a5f14dd5f8ed2b2a4d35491cfd9.poster.avif?t=1766090307\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069160/extras/50683a5f14dd5f8ed2b2a4d35491cfd9.webm?t=1766090307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069160/extras/50683a5f14dd5f8ed2b2a4d35491cfd9.mp4?t=1766090307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >组建团队</h2>带领一众落魄英雄，应对高难度回合制战斗，冷热兵器任你选，强拼巧避随你定，只为智取凶恶悍敌。现代背包系统里走一遭，英雄就能披挂上阵；战斗与任务日志翻一遍，逐一完成目标，揭开尘封已久的秘密。如果还是寸步难行，大可随心调整难度，玩得惬意最重要。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069160/extras/c6ce544ebe8656f83b5895b26d0196e0.poster.avif?t=1766090307\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069160/extras/c6ce544ebe8656f83b5895b26d0196e0.webm?t=1766090307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069160/extras/c6ce544ebe8656f83b5895b26d0196e0.mp4?t=1766090307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >准备万全</h2>自由选择角色属性，按需招募同伴。形形色色的角色，各有各的特长，各有各的想法，各有各的性格，最高可达20级。十几种职业和出身，再加大量法术和装备，混搭空间十足。别忘了手头还有精选远洋菜谱，助你化身巧匠大厨，为冒险之旅做好物资储备。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069160/extras/5e14d27b4cdb4641f510841d31824308.poster.avif?t=1766090307\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069160/extras/5e14d27b4cdb4641f510841d31824308.webm?t=1766090307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069160/extras/5e14d27b4cdb4641f510841d31824308.mp4?t=1766090307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一往无前</h2>世界冷酷无情，洛夫克拉夫特式恐怖如影随形，一次次选择交织出专属于你的曲折故事线。堕入险境或是侥幸生还，这道雇佣兵生活中时时可见的选择题，就让手中骰子来决定吧。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069160/extras/7e4aae14d70bc3c73d0fd07fc64bc5b0.poster.avif?t=1766090307\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069160/extras/7e4aae14d70bc3c73d0fd07fc64bc5b0.webm?t=1766090307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069160/extras/7e4aae14d70bc3c73d0fd07fc64bc5b0.mp4?t=1766090307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >追忆往昔</h2>揭晓加里安帝国的宏图大计，探索辽阔的弗雷麦与外岛。在《SKALD：攻打黑修院》中，你可以体验到丰富多彩的像素世界，千万方格均为手绘，用色则借鉴了传奇电脑“康懋达64”，还可以选择 CRT 滤镜，获得货真价实的复古体验。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >模组支持</h2>想要继续拓展《SKALD：攻打黑修院》的玩法？没问题！我们目前推出了 SKALD 数据编辑工具（SKaDE），方便玩家创建专属冒险之旅，还可以免费体验其他玩家分享的新内容。这款自由度极高的模组工具由 Mod.io 提供技术支持，玩家可以访问《SKALD：攻打黑修院》的所有资产，尽情挥洒天马行空的想象力。",
